---
import Terminal from "./ui/Terminal.astro";
---

<section class="py-24 bg-bg-base">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="text-center mb-16 reveal">
      <p class="section-label">CLI + Mobile</p>
      <h2 class="mb-4">Terminal-first. Phone when you need it.</h2>
      <p class="body-lg max-w-[560px] mx-auto text-text-secondary">
        oru is a CLI tool. That is its primary interface and it always will be.
        But tasks follow you. The native iOS app exists for those moments.
      </p>
    </div>

    <div class="grid grid-cols-2 gap-12 items-start max-md:grid-cols-1">
      <div class="min-w-0 reveal" data-delay="80">
        <h3 class="text-[22px] mb-3">
          Pair with a QR code. No accounts required.
        </h3>
        <p class="body text-text-secondary mb-3">
          Run <code
            class="font-mono text-[13px] bg-bg-surface px-1.5 py-0.5 rounded text-accent"
            >oru server start</code
          >. A QR code appears in your terminal. Scan it with the iOS app. You
          are connected over your local network. That is the entire pairing flow.
        </p>
        <p class="body-sm text-text-tertiary mb-6">
          No cloud relay. No account creation. No sync service to configure. The
          phone talks directly to your machine.
        </p>
        <Terminal title="oru server start">
          <span class="line"><span class="prompt">$ </span><span class="cmd">oru</span> <span class="sub">server</span> <span class="sub">start</span></span>
          <span class="blank"></span>
          <span class="line"><span class="output">Server running on http://192.168.1.42:3000</span></span>
          <span class="blank"></span>
          <span class="line"><span class="output">Scan this QR code with the oru iOS app:</span></span>
          <span class="blank"></span>
          <span class="line qr-art"><span class="output"> ▄▄▄▄▄▄▄ ▄▄  ▄ ▄▄▄▄▄▄▄ </span></span>
          <span class="line qr-art"><span class="output"> █ ▄▄▄ █ ▄▀▀█▄ █ ▄▄▄ █ </span></span>
          <span class="line qr-art"><span class="output"> █ ███ █ ▀█▄▀▄ █ ███ █ </span></span>
          <span class="line qr-art"><span class="output"> █▄▄▄▄▄█ █ █ █ █▄▄▄▄▄█ </span></span>
          <span class="line qr-art"><span class="output"> ▄▄ ▄  ▄▄▄▀▀▄▄▄ ▄▄ ▄ ▄ </span></span>
          <span class="line qr-art"><span class="output"> ▄▀▀▄▀▄▄▀▄█ ▀▄▄▀▄▄▀ █▀ </span></span>
          <span class="line qr-art"><span class="output"> ▄▀█ ▀▄ ▀▄ █▀▄▄█ █▀▄▄▀ </span></span>
          <span class="line qr-art"><span class="output"> ▄▄▄▄▄▄▄ ▄▀▄▄▀▄▀▀▄▀▄▄▀ </span></span>
          <span class="line qr-art"><span class="output"> █ ▄▄▄ █ ▀█ ▄▀▄▀▀▄▀▄▄▀ </span></span>
          <span class="line qr-art"><span class="output"> █ ███ █ ▀ █▄▀▄▄▀▄▀ ▄▀ </span></span>
          <span class="line qr-art"><span class="output"> █▄▄▄▄▄█ █▀ ▄▀▄▄█▄▀▀▄▀ </span></span>
          <span class="blank"></span>
          <span class="line"><span class="output">Waiting for connection...</span></span>
        </Terminal>
      </div>

      <div class="reveal" data-delay="240">
        <h3 class="text-[22px] mb-3">Native iOS, not a web view.</h3>
        <p class="body text-text-secondary mb-3">
          SwiftUI components. SF Symbols. System colors. Haptic feedback. The
          app is built with Expo and React Native but renders native controls.
        </p>
        <div
          class="mt-6 bg-black border-2 border-border-default rounded-[40px] p-3 max-w-[320px] mx-auto shadow-[0_0_0_1px_rgba(255,255,255,0.05),0_8px_40px_rgba(0,0,0,0.5)]"
        >
          <div
            class="w-[120px] h-7 bg-black rounded-b-2xl mx-auto mb-2 relative z-1"
          ></div>
          <div
            class="bg-bg-base rounded-[28px] overflow-hidden min-h-[480px] flex flex-col"
          >
            <div
              class="flex justify-between items-baseline pt-4 pb-3 px-5"
            >
              <span class="text-[28px] font-bold text-text-primary"
                >Tasks</span
              >
              <span class="text-[13px] text-text-tertiary">3 items</span>
            </div>
            <div class="flex-1 px-3">
              <div
                class="flex items-start gap-3 py-3.5 px-2 border-b border-border-subtle"
              >
                <div
                  class="w-[22px] h-[22px] rounded-full bg-accent border-2 border-accent shrink-0 mt-px"
                ></div>
                <div class="flex flex-col gap-[3px] min-w-0">
                  <span
                    class="text-[15px] text-text-tertiary font-medium line-through"
                    >Refactor auth middleware</span
                  >
                  <span
                    class="text-xs text-text-tertiary flex items-center gap-1"
                    ><span
                      class="w-1.5 h-1.5 rounded-full bg-[#ef4444] inline-block"
                    ></span> high &middot; Fri Feb 20</span
                  >
                </div>
              </div>
              <div
                class="flex items-start gap-3 py-3.5 px-2 border-b border-border-subtle"
              >
                <div
                  class="w-[22px] h-[22px] rounded-full border-2 border-syn-command bg-[rgba(96,165,250,0.15)] shrink-0 mt-px"
                ></div>
                <div class="flex flex-col gap-[3px] min-w-0">
                  <span class="text-[15px] text-text-primary font-medium"
                    >Write migration tests</span
                  >
                  <span
                    class="text-xs text-text-tertiary flex items-center gap-1"
                    ><span
                      class="w-1.5 h-1.5 rounded-full bg-accent inline-block"
                    ></span> medium</span
                  >
                </div>
              </div>
              <div
                class="flex items-start gap-3 py-3.5 px-2 border-b border-border-subtle"
              >
                <div
                  class="w-[22px] h-[22px] rounded-full border-2 border-border-default shrink-0 mt-px"
                ></div>
                <div class="flex flex-col gap-[3px] min-w-0">
                  <span class="text-[15px] text-text-primary font-medium"
                    >Update API docs</span
                  >
                  <span
                    class="text-xs text-text-tertiary flex items-center gap-1"
                    ><span
                      class="w-1.5 h-1.5 rounded-full bg-syn-command inline-block"
                    ></span> low</span
                  >
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>
            <div
              class="flex border-t border-border-subtle pt-2 pb-5"
            >
              <div
                class="flex-1 flex flex-col items-center gap-1 text-accent text-[10px]"
              >
                <svg
                  width="18"
                  height="18"
                  viewBox="0 0 24 24"
                  fill="none"
                  stroke="currentColor"
                  stroke-width="2"
                  ><path d="M9 11l3 3L22 4"></path><path
                    d="M21 12v7a2 2 0 0 1-2 2H5a2 2 0 0 1-2-2V5a2 2 0 0 1 2-2h11"
                  ></path></svg
                >
                <span>Tasks</span>
              </div>
              <div
                class="flex-1 flex flex-col items-center gap-1 text-text-muted text-[10px]"
              >
                <svg
                  width="18"
                  height="18"
                  viewBox="0 0 24 24"
                  fill="none"
                  stroke="currentColor"
                  stroke-width="2"
                  ><circle cx="12" cy="12" r="3"></circle><path
                    d="M19.4 15a1.65 1.65 0 0 0 .33 1.82l.06.06a2 2 0 0 1 0 2.83 2 2 0 0 1-2.83 0l-.06-.06a1.65 1.65 0 0 0-1.82-.33 1.65 1.65 0 0 0-1 1.51V21a2 2 0 0 1-2 2 2 2 0 0 1-2-2v-.09A1.65 1.65 0 0 0 9 19.4a1.65 1.65 0 0 0-1.82.33l-.06.06a2 2 0 0 1-2.83 0 2 2 0 0 1 0-2.83l.06-.06A1.65 1.65 0 0 0 4.68 15a1.65 1.65 0 0 0-1.51-1H3a2 2 0 0 1-2-2 2 2 0 0 1 2-2h.09A1.65 1.65 0 0 0 4.6 9a1.65 1.65 0 0 0-.33-1.82l-.06-.06a2 2 0 0 1 0-2.83 2 2 0 0 1 2.83 0l.06.06A1.65 1.65 0 0 0 9 4.68a1.65 1.65 0 0 0 1-1.51V3a2 2 0 0 1 2-2 2 2 0 0 1 2 2v.09a1.65 1.65 0 0 0 1 1.51 1.65 1.65 0 0 0 1.82-.33l.06-.06a2 2 0 0 1 2.83 0 2 2 0 0 1 0 2.83l-.06.06A1.65 1.65 0 0 0 19.4 9a1.65 1.65 0 0 0 1.51 1H21a2 2 0 0 1 2 2 2 2 0 0 1-2 2h-.09a1.65 1.65 0 0 0-1.51 1z"
                  ></path></svg
                >
                <span>Settings</span>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .qr-art {
    font-size: 10px !important;
    line-height: 1 !important;
    letter-spacing: 0 !important;
  }
</style>
